+- PASS: Theme V2 HTML restrictions preserved. Evidence: `rg --pcre2 -n "<script(?![^>]*\\bsrc=)|<style\\b|\\son[a-z]+\\s*=" toolbox/assets/index.html toolbox/tags/index.html` returned no matches.
